SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]

    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]

    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]

    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]

2025-01-04 20:06:07.271 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (6ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

2025-01-04 20:13:25.254 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (6ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]

) AS [t]

FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]

        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]

        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

2025-01-04 22:37:54.402 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (18ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

2025-01-04 22:43:20.734 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (19ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]

2025-01-04 22:46:57.489 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (5ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Description], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Category], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Name], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[UpdatedDate], [c].[Category]
    FROM [Courses] AS [c]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [c0].[CourseImageFilesId], [c0].[CoursesId]
    FROM [CourseCourseImageFile] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'CourseImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [c0].[CourseImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CoursesId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[CourseImageFilesId], [t0].[CoursesId]
